# Use TextStyle extensions

- Apply text style like this const TextStyle().setH1.setBlackColor

- For Colors :
    - if Color Hex not exist in the file [color_manager.dart](mdc:lib/src/config/res/color_manager.dart) then add it in file [color_manager.dart](mdc:lib/src/config/res/color_manager.dart) like this:
        static const Color colorNameBasedOnValue = Color(0xff009B4D);
    -Go to File [text_style_extensions.dart](mdc:lib/src/core/extensions/text_style_extensions.dart) then declare the new TextStyle getter Like this
        TextStyle get setPrimaryColor => copyWith(color: AppColors.primary);
        

